      "body": "<p class=\"question\"></p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n<p>\n            Zarówno prostokąt jak i kwadrat są równoległobokami. \n        </p>\n<p>\n            Jak wyglądają wzory na pola prostokąta i kwadratu w zależności od długości przekątnych?\n        </p>\n<div class=\"important\">\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\n<div style=\"min-width: 300px; width: 50%;\">\n<figure>\n<img src=\"static/prostokat_pole_przekatne.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; max-height: 250px;\"/>\n</figure>\n<details>\n<summary>pole <strong>prostokąta</strong></summary>\n<p>\n                            \\(P\\), pole prostokąta o przekątnych długości \\(d\\) i kącie między nimi o mierze \\(\\beta\\) jest dane wzorem\n                        </p>\n                        \\[\n                        P=\\frac{1}{2}d^2\\sin\\beta\n                        \\]\n                    </details>\n</div>\n<div style=\"min-width: 300px; width: 50%;\">\n<figure>\n<img src=\"static/kwadrat_pole_przekatne.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; max-height: 250px;\"/>\n</figure>\n<details>\n<summary>pole <strong>kwadratu</strong></summary>\n<p>\n                            \\(P\\), pole kwadratu o przekątnych długości \\(d\\) jest dane wzorem\n                        </p>\n                        \\[\n                        P=\\frac{1}{2}d^2\n                        \\]\n                    </details>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p class=\"question\"></p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n<p>\n            Pole kwadratu o przekątnej długości \\(d\\) jest równe \\(P\\).\n        </p>\n<div class=\"switch_steps\">\n<div class=\"switch_step\">\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n<strong>1.</strong> Jeśli \\(d=6\\), to \\(P=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">&gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(36\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(18\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(9\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">zatwierdź</div>.\n                </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n<strong>2.</strong> Jeśli \\(d=7\\), to \\(P=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">&gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(49\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(\\tfrac{49}{2}\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(\\tfrac{49}{4}\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">zatwierdź</div>.\n                </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n<strong>3.</strong> Jeśli \\(P=8\\), to \\(d=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">&gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(2\\sqrt{2}\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(4\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(4\\sqrt{2}\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(8\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">zatwierdź</div>.\n                </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n<strong>4.</strong> Jeśli \\(P=25\\), to \\(d=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">&gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(5\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(5\\sqrt{2}\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(10\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\\(10\\sqrt{2}\\)</div>\n<div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">zatwierdź</div>.\n                </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Świetnie!\n            </div>\n</div>\n"
    },
    {
